<robot>
  <background_image>megascout_back.png</background_image>
  <short_name>MegaScout</short_name>
  <long_name>The MegaScout Robot</long_name>
  <description>The MegaScout is a wholly new robot platform developed at the University of Minnesota to work in conjunction with a Scout team. The MegaScout is intended to provide command and control support for a Scout team as well as perform independently. The MegaScouts are still in their early prototyping stages, and more information will be provided as it becomes available.</description>
